A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Title 13 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to contracts, so as to
2 make certain disclosure and notification requirements concerning automatic renewal
3 provisions applicable to service contracts with small businesses; to revise and provide for
4 definitions; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 Title 13 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to contracts, is amended by
8 revising Chapter 12, relating to automatic renewal provisions, as follows:
9 "CHAPTER 12
10 13-12-1.
11 As used in this chapter, the term:
12 (1) 'Automatic renewal provision' means a provision under which a service contract is
13 renewed for a specified period of more than one month if the renewal causes the service
14 contract to be in effect more than six months after the day of the initiation of the service
